    <h1 class="tt-hero-title">Thesis<br><em>Tracker</em></h1>
    <p class="tt-hero-lede">
      An AI research agent that builds, scores, and tracks investment theses. Give it an idea. Five agents source the filings, argue both sides, score conviction, and draft a dated memo in my voice. Then it logs the idea and measures how my conviction drifts over time.
    </p>
    <p class="tt-hero-provenance">
      This is the same multi-agent workflow engine I built to run my own job search end to end, pointed at markets instead. I did not just use an AI tool. I built one, and I can tell you where it is wrong. It also runs as the /thesis skill inside the <a href="/workbench" class="tt-provenance-link">Desk Workbench</a>, the agent operating system on this site.
    </p>
